{"tid":698281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］有冇巴絲有面對屋企人有精神病嘅經驗","createTime":"2018-06-11T14:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T18:07:24.000Z","uid":20836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d22756407a5a45fd189babbbeb932a5cb16ecf","tid":698281,"uid":20836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:13:42.000Z","msg":"話說最近識咗個女仔，同個女仔都叫啱傾<br />\n<br />\n傾耐咗之後發現，原來佢阿媽係有精神病<br />\n<br />\n耐唔耐就會斬鳩個女，唔係之前某巴打嘅老豆<br />\n<br />\n剩係講但係冇斬，佢阿媽真係拎刀斬鳩個女嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n所以佢由中學開始已經冇理過個阿媽<br />\n<br />\n而佢仲讀緊書，冇能力自己搬出嚟住<br />\n<br />\n搞到佢成日都好驚自己有日畀佢阿媽斬死<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有冇啲類似嘅經驗或者方法可以拆掂佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78071638c13e3840565cb62ec4ec9014e4edd01d","tid":698281,"uid":20836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:14:06.000Z","msg":"佢成日都喺度諗呢件事，搞到自己嘅生活亂曬<br />\n<br />\n好想可以幫下佢，但係我真係唔知可以點幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bf8471e325fcf0bc2a51a760b9c9908e0f27d8","tid":698281,"uid":20836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:17:24.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"83778761a9e4014375aba9347cfa5b0819559b2c","tid":698281,"uid":20836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"59f5c3c3724240611881564b5bf0c66005500bc8","tid":698281,"uid":20836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:17:54.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c7c6c8438a84c2ae8f15b51b5881f9b6ca5ad140","tid":698281,"uid":20836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:18:12.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"f10ccfc2efc2be26ca88ac5457c96a1958990359","tid":698281,"uid":20836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"dd04834d80ef50ef7f83ffa008783d8c288b1f14","tid":698281,"uid":20836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:18:33.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"a5